OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Chancellor Jeremy Hunt has said he     
OL,6, wants to move towards lower taxes, but 
OL,7, will only do so in "a responsible way".
OL,9,FHe told the BBC it would be            
OL,10,F"unconservative" to cut taxes by       
OL,11,Fincreasing borrowing.                  
OL,13,FMr Hunt is under pressure from some    
OL,14,FTory MPs to reduce taxes in Wednesday's
OL,15,FBudget, ahead of a general election    
OL,16,Fthat must take place by January.       
OL,18,FA further cut to National Insurance is 
OL,19,Fbelieved to be among the measures being
OL,20,Fconsidered by the chancellor.          
